Basil of Baker Street and some non-fanart...

I draw Disney every once in awhile. Really.

http://www.geocities.com/tiamat61185/site/basilsketch.txt

Basil from The Great Mouse Detective. I used to love that movie Haven't seen it in ages though. The pose for this drawing was referenced off an image I printed from the internet (just so I can get his design down). Once I get this drawing finished, I'll go draw him in an original pose.

And, to prove I don't just draw fanart all the time...

http://www.geocities.com/tiamat61185/site/logodesign1.txt

Just an assignment for one of my design classes. Draw and color some logos depicting emotions. Unfinished at the moment.
